  "prompt": "Which is the best training institute for spoken English in Pune?",
  "response": "There are several reputable institutes for spoken English training in Pune. While the \"best\" can vary based on individual preferences, here are some popular options:\n\n1. **Spoken English Institute** - Known for its comprehensive courses and experienced instructors.\n2. **British Council** - Offers high-quality English language training with a global reputation.\n3. **Inlingua** - Focuses on practical language skills and conversational English.\n4. **ACE English Academy** - Offers personalized training and flexible courses tailored to individual needs.\n5. **Pune Institute of Business Management (PIBM)** - Provides spoken English courses along with other skills.\n\nIt's advisable to visit the institutes, check reviews, and consider factors like course content, duration, faculty qualifications, and fees before making a decision.",
